1. Datamining
1.1. go to storage/emulated/legacy/android/data/
1.2. copy folder com.aniplex.monogataripucpuc 
1.3. paste to mnt/shared/other
1.4. find path on pc via the "File Transfer" action
1.5. use AssetStudio to get images from files

2. Scene Manupulation
2.1. Crop
2.1.1. go to https://birme.net/
2.1.2. cut images to 1200x745 without auto detect
2.1.3. save as zip
2.2. Rezise
2.2.1. go to https://bulkresizephotos.com/
2.2.2. set to pro
2.2.3. set to Resize = 50%
2.2.4. save as .png